2 - SDM scripts

01_SDM_Random_Forest: The first step inputs the phenology & range data into a series of BIOMOD2 functions to output species-level predictions. Important outputs from this script include spatial projections (tif & csv). 

02_Error_Propagation: This script uses only the projection data as inputs to calculate the mean and standard deviation of the projected SDM ouputs.  


Please be mindful of the directories used and naming conventions, adjust accordingly. 